name: Admiration
description:
What I love about street photography is that everytime you go home from a walk, you don’t know what kind of photographs you’ll end up with.
 Keeping expectations low and preparing yourself for a pleasant surprise or a huge disappointment makes this genre a thrilling and exciting one.

What I’ve learnt is to admire every single thing that passes by.

Finding beauty in every little thing.

-

Captured in Kyoto, Japan
